devdoc.title: Proxyable Contract sits behind a Proxy

renounceOwnership().notice: Renouncing to ownership will leave the contract without an owner. It will not be possible to call the functions with the `onlyOwner` modifier anymore.

userdoc.notice: A proxyable contract that works hand in hand with the Proxy contract to allow for anyone to interact with the underlying contract both  directly and through the proxy. This contract should be treated like an abstract contract. Simply inherit  Proxyable on the target contract.
